Package totalcross

Package used to emulate TotalCross when running at the desktop on the top of a Java Virtual Machine.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MainClass
    This is the main class of a TotalCross package.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Launcher
    Represents the applet or application used as a Java Container to make possible run TotalCross at the desktop.
    Launcher.CharBits
    Represents the internal font structure, read from a pdb file. used internally.
    Launcher.IS2S
    Converts a java.io.InputStream into a totalcross.io.Stream
